crashTag.label: Crash Tag
crashTag.description: Unique tag of the crash dataset

partyTag.label: Party Tag
partyTag.description: Unique tag of the party dataset

victimTag.label: Victim Tag
victimTag.description: Unique tag of the victim dataset

partyNumber.label: Party Number
partyNumber.description: A number that together with the Case ID uniquely identifies a party in a crash

victimNumber.label: Victim Number
victimNumber.description: A number that together with the Case ID uniquely identifies a victim in a crash

crashesCaseTag.label: Crashes Tag
crashesCaseTag.description: Total number of crashes per case

partiesCaseTag.label: Parties Tag
partiesCaseTag.description: Total number of parties per case

victimsCaseTag.label: Victims Tag
victimsCaseTag.description: Total number of victims per case

crashesInd.label: Crashes Indicator
crashesInd.description: Indicator variable for the unique crashes in the dataset

parties_ind.label: Parties Indicator
parties_ind.description: Indicator variable for the unique parties in the dataset

victimsInd.label: Victims Indicator
victimsInd.description: Indicator variable for the unique victims in the dataset

crashesCidCount.label: Total Collisions in Crashes Dataset
crashesCidCount.description: Total number of collisions in the crashes dataset

partiesCidCount.label: Total Collisions in Parties Dataset
partiesCidCount.description: Total number of collisions in the parties dataset

victimsCidCount.label: Total Collisions in Victims Dataset
victimsCidCount.description: Total number of collisions in the victims dataset

partiesPidCount.label: Total Parties in Parties Dataset
partiesPidCount.description: Total number of parties in the parties dataset

victimsPidCount.label: Total Parties in Victims Dataset
victimsPidCount.description: Total number of parties in the victims dataset

victimsVidCount.label: Total Victims in Victims Dataset
victimsVidCount.description: Total number of victims in the victims dataset

dateDatetime.label: Crash Date and Time
dateDatetime.description: Date and time of the crash case
dateDatetime.varNotes: Generated by lubridate: as.POSIXlt(paste(crashes$coll_date, crashes$coll_time_temp), format = '%Y-%m-%d %H:%M', tz = 'America/Los_Angeles')

dateYear.label: Crash Year
dateYear.description: First day of the year of the crash case

dateQuarter.label: Crash Quarter
dateQuarter.description: First day of the quarter of the crash case

dateMonth.label: Crash Month
dateMonth.description: First day of the month of the crash case

dateWeek.label: Crash Week
dateWeek.description: First day of the week of the crash case

dateProcess.label: Process Date
dateProcess.varNotes: Generated by lubridate: as.POSIXlt(crashes$process_date, format = '%Y-%m-%d', tz = 'America/Los_Angeles')

dtYearWeek.label: Crash Year Week
dtYearWeek.description: Year week of the crash case

dtMonthDay.label: Crash Month Day
dtMonthDay.description: Month day of the crash case

dtYearDay.label: Crash Year Day
dtYearDay.description: Year day of the crash case

dtDst.label: Crash Daylight Saving Time
dtDst.description: Daylight saving time of the crash case

dtZone.label: Crash Time Zone
dtZone.description: Time zone of the crash case

collDate.label: Collision Date Reported
collDate.description: Collision date reported and recorded at the scene of the accident

collTime.label: Collision Time Reported
collTime.description: The time when the crash occurred in 24h format

accidentYear.label: Crash Year
accidentYear.description: The year when the crash occurred

processDate.label: Processing Date
processDate.description: The date that the crash case was last changed

rushHours.label: Rush Hours
rushHours.description: Rush hours interval ranges (Mon-Fri mornings and evenings)

collSeverity.label: Collision Severity
collSeverity.description: The worst injury suffered by any victim in the crash

collSeverityNum.label: Collision Severity Numeric
collSeverityNum.description: Numeric representation of the worst injury suffered by any victim in the crash

collSeverityBin.label: Collision Severity Binary
collSeverityBin.description: Binary classification of the worst injury suffered by any victim in the crash

collSeverityRank.label: Collision Severity Rank
collSeverityRank.description: Ranked crash severity based on the worst injury suffered by any victim in the crash

collSeverityRankNum.label: Collision Severity Rank Numeric
collSeverityRankNum.description: Numeric representation of the ranked crash severity based on the worst injury suffered by any victim in the crash

indSevere.label: Severe Injury Indicator
indSevere.description: Reclassified indicator variable from severity level where there exist severe injuries in the accident

indFatal.label: Fatal Injury Indicator
indFatal.description: Reclassified indicator variable from severity level where there exist fatal injuries in the accident

indMulti.label: Multiple Injury Indicator
indMulti.description: Reclassified indicator variable from severity level where there exist multiple injuries or fatalities in the accident

partyCount.label: Party Count
partyCount.description: Total number of parties involved in the crash

victimCount.label: Victim Count
victimCount.description: Total number of victims involved in the crash

countSevereInj.label: Severe Injury Count
countSevereInj.description: Number of victims in the crash with suspected serous injury or severe injury

countVisibleInj.label: Visible Injury Count
countVisibleInj.description: Number of victims in the crash with suspected minor injury or visible injury

countComplaintPain.label: Complaint of Pain Injury Count
countComplaintPain.description: Number of victims in the crash with possible injury or complaint of pain

countCarKilled.label: Number of Killed Car Victims
countCarKilled.description: Number of killed car victims (drivers or passengers)

countCarInj.label: Number of Injured Car Victims
countCarInj.description: Number of injured car victims (drivers or passengers)

primaryCollFactor.label: Primary Collision Factor
primaryCollFactor.description: The primary collision factor that caused the crash

typeOfColl.label: Type of Crash
typeOfColl.description: The general type of crash as determined by the first injury or damage-causing event

pedAccident.label: Pedestrian Crash
pedAccident.description: Indicates whether the crash involved a pedestrian

bicAccident.label: Bicycle Crash
bicAccident.description: Indicates whether the crash involved a bicycle

mcAccident.label: Motorcycle Crash
mcAccident.description: Indicates whether the crash involved a motorcycle

truckAccident.label: Truck Crash
truckAccident.description: Indicates whether the crash involved a big truck

hitAndRun.label: Hit and Run
hitAndRun.description: A flag to indicate the severity of hit-and-run crash. Felony hit-and-run resulted in injury or death to other parties. Misdemeanor hit-and-run did not result in injury or death to other parties

hitAndRunBin.label: Hit and Run Binary
hitAndRunBin.description: Whether the accident involved hit and run (recoded)

alcoholInvolved.label: Alcohol Involved
alcoholInvolved.description: Indicates whether the crash involved a party that had been drinking. Note - a passenger does not count as a party

juris.label: Jurisdiction
juris.description: Law enforcement agency that has jurisdiction over the crash

officerId.label: Officer ID
officerId.description: The badge number of the officer who wrote the crash report

reportingDistrict.label: Reporting District
reportingDistrict.description: Reporting District on the crash report

chpShift.label: CHP Shift
chpShift.description: CHP shift at the time of the crash

cntyCityLoc.label: County City Location
cntyCityLoc.description: The city or unincorporated county where the crash occurred

specialCond.label: Special Condition
specialCond.description: A computed value. O means not private property

beatType.label: Beat Type
beatType.description: Location of crash based on beat

chpBeatType.label: CHP Beat Type
chpBeatType.description: Location of crash based on CHP beat

chpBeatClass.label: CHP Beat Class
chpBeatClass.description: Location of crash based on CHP beat class

beatNumber.label: Beat Number
beatNumber.description: Beat of the officer who reported the crash

primaryRd.label: Primary Road
primaryRd.description: The name of the roadway on which the crash occurred

secondaryRd.label: Secondary Road
secondaryRd.description: The name of the roadway that intersects the primary roadway

distance.label: Distance
distance.description: Distance of the crash from the intersection with the secondary roadway in ft

direction.label: Direction
direction.description: Direction of travel of the primary party

intersection.label: Intersection
intersection.description: A flag that denotes if the crash occurred at the intersection with the secondary roadway
intersection.varNotes: Aggregation only if the intersection is 1 (Yes)

weather1.label: Weather 1
weather1.description: Weather condition at the time of the crash

weather2.label: Weather 2
weather2.description: Additional weather condition at the time of the crash

weatherComb.label: Combined Weather
weatherComb.description: Combined Weather Conditions from WEATHER_1 and WEATHER_2 fields in numeric codes by weather conditions severity

roadSurface.label: Road Surface
roadSurface.description: Roadway surface condition at the time of the crash in the traffic lane(s) involved

roadCond1.label: Road Condition 1
roadCond1.description: Roadway condition at the time of the crash in the traffic lane(s) involved

roadCond2.label: Road Condition 2
roadCond2.description: Second roadway condition at the time of the crash in the traffic lane(s) involved

lighting.label: Lighting
lighting.description: Lighting conditions at the crash location and the time of the crash

controlDevice.label: Control Device
controlDevice.description: Presence and condition of crash related traffic control devices at the time of the crash. Control devices include regulatory, warning, and construction sings. This excludes striping and officers or other persons directing traffic
controlDevice.varNotes: aggregate if the control device is 2 (Not Functioning) or 3 (Obscured)

stateHwyInd.label: State Highway Indicator
stateHwyInd.description: A flag to indicate whether the crash is on or near a state highway
stateHwyInd.varNotes: aggregate if the state highway indicator is 1 (State Highway)

sideOfHwy.label: Side of Highway
sideOfHwy.description: Code provided by Caltrans Coders, applies to divided highway, based on nominal direction of route, for single vehicle is same as nominal direction of travel, overruled by impact with second vehicle after crossing median

towAway.label: Tow Away
towAway.description: A flag to indicate whether the vehicle was towed away from the crash scene
towAway.varNotes: aggregate if the tow away indicator is 1 (Yes)

pcfCodeOfViol.label: PCF Violation Code
pcfCodeOfViol.description: he law code that was violated and was the primary cause of the crash

pcfViolCategory.label: PCF Violation Category
pcfViolCategory.description: A value computed from the law section that was given as the primary cause of the crash

pcfViolation.label: PCF Violation
pcfViolation.description: The law section given as the primary cause of the crash. The subsection is in the data element pcf_viol_subsection

pcfViolSubsection.label: PCF Violation Subsection
pcfViolSubsection.description: The subsection of the law section given as the primary cause of the crash in the data element pcf_violation

mviw.label: Motor Vehicle Involved With
mviw.description: Describes what, in conjunction with a motor vehicle in-transport, produced the first injury or damage-causing event, on or off the road

pedAction.label: Pedestrian Action
pedAction.description: The action just prior to the crash of the first pedestrian injured or otherwise involved

notPrivateProperty.label: Not Private Property
notPrivateProperty.description: Y indicates that the crash did not occur on private property

stwdVehTypeAtFault.label: Statewide Vehicle Type at Fault
stwdVehTypeAtFault.description: Indicates the statewide vehicle type of the party who is at fault

chpVehTypeAtFault.label: CHP Vehicle Type at Fault
chpVehTypeAtFault.description: Indicates the CHP vehicle type of the party who is at fault

primaryRamp.label: Primary Ramp
primaryRamp.description: A description of the ramp, if any, on primary roadway. This value is computed by the key operator from information on the crash report

secondaryRamp.label: Secondary Ramp
secondaryRamp.description: A description of the ramp, if any, on secondary roadway. This value is computed by the key operator from information on the crash report

partyType.label: Party Type
partyType.description: The type of party involved in the crash

atFault.label: At Fault
atFault.description: Indicates whether the party was at fault in the crash

partyAge.label: Party Age
partyAge.description: The age of the party at the time of the crash

partyAgeGroup.label: Party Age Group
partyAgeGroup.description: The age group of the party at the time of the crash

partyRace.label: Party Race
partyRace.description: The party's race based on the reporting officer's judgment
partyRace.varNotes: aggregate for each of the race categories separately

partyNumberKilled.label: Party Number Killed
partyNumberKilled.description: Number of killed victims in the party

partyNumberInj.label: Party Number Injured
partyNumberInj.description: Number of injured victims in the party

inattention.label: Inattention
inattention.description: Type of inattention by the party at the time of the crash

partySobriety.label: Party Sobriety
partySobriety.description: The sobriety of the party at the time of the crash

duiAlcoholInd.label: DUI Alcohol Indicator
duiAlcoholInd.description: Indicates whether the party was under the influence of alcohol at the time of the crash

partyDrugPhysical.label: Party Drug Physical
partyDrugPhysical.description: The state of the party with regard to drugs and physical condition

duiDrugInd.label: DUI Drug Indicator
duiDrugInd.description: Indicates whether the party was under the influence of drugs at the time of the crash

dirOfTravel.label: Direction of Travel
dirOfTravel.description: Direction that the party was traveling at the time of the crash

partySafetyEq1.label: Party Safety Equipment 1
partySafetyEq1.description: The safety equipment used by the party

partySafetyEq2.label: Party Safety Equipment 2
partySafetyEq2.description: The safety equipment used by the party

spInfo1.label: Special Information 1
spInfo1.description: Value A indicates that the crash involved in a vehicle known to be, or believed to be, transporting a hazardous material as defined in CVC Section 353, whether or not the crash involved a hazardous material incident

spInfo3.label: Special Information 3
spInfo3.description: Value E indicates that the crash involved a motor vehicle in-transport passing a stopped school bus with its red signal lamps in operation pursuant to CVC Section 22112, or reacting to, pursuant to CVC Section 22454

oafViolCode.label: OAF Violation Code
oafViolCode.description: Other associated factor law code violated

oafViolCat.label: OAF Violation Category
oafViolCat.description: Category of the factor that contributed to the crash but was not the primary cause of the crash

oafViolSection.label: OAF Violation Section
oafViolSection.description: The CVC section of the secondary violation that contributed to the crash

oafViolSuffix.label: OAF Violation Suffix
oafViolSuffix.description: The subsection of the CVC section of the secondary violation that contributed to the crash

oaf1.label: Other Associated Factor 1
oaf1.description: A factor that contributed to the crash but was not the primary cause of the crash

oaf2.label: Other Associated Factor 2
oaf2.description: A factor that contributed to the crash but was not the primary cause of the crash

movePreAcc.label: Movement Preceding Crash
movePreAcc.description: The action of the vehicle prior to the crash and before evasive action. This movement does not have to correspond with the PCF

vehicleYear.label: Vehicle Year
vehicleYear.description: The model year of the party's vehicle

vehicleYearGroup.label: Vehicle Year Group
vehicleYearGroup.description: The model year group of the party's vehicle
vehicleYearGroup.varNotes: aggregation of the mean decade of the vehicle year - higher indicates newer

vehicleMake.label: Vehicle Make
vehicleMake.description: The make of the party's vehicle

stwdVehicleType.label: Statewide Vehicle Type
stwdVehicleType.description: Type of the party's vehicle according to a list called statewide vehicle type

chpVehTypeTowing.label: CHP Vehicle Type Towing
chpVehTypeTowing.description: The type of the solitary vehicle or the tractor unit according to the CHP manual HPM 110.5 Chapter 3 Annex F vehicle type codes

chpVehTypeTowed.label: CHP Vehicle Type Towed
chpVehTypeTowed.description: The type of the first trailer unit according to the CHP manual HPM 110.5 Chapter 3 Annex F vehicle type codes

specialInfoF.label: Special Information F
specialInfoF.description: The value F indicate that the party's vehicle is a 75ft motor truck combo

specialInfoG.label: Special Information G
specialInfoG.description: The value G indicate that the party's vehicle is a 48ft motor truck combo

victimAge.label: Victim Age
victimAge.description: The age of the victim at the time of the crash
victimAge.varNotes: aggregate if it is less than 990

victimAgeGroup.label: Victim Age Group
victimAgeGroup.description: The age group of the victim at the time of the crash

victimDegreeOfInjury.label: Victim Degree of Injury
victimDegreeOfInjury.description: The severity of the injury to the victim
victimDegreeOfInjury.varNotes: aggregate if it is not 9 - higher meeans more severe

victimDegreeOfInjuryBin.label: Victim Degree of Injury Binary
victimDegreeOfInjuryBin.description: Binary classification of the severity of the injury to the victim

victimSeatingPosition.label: Victim Seating Position
victimSeatingPosition.description: The seating position of the victim

victimSafetyEq1.label: Victim Safety Equipment 1
victimSafetyEq1.description: The safety equipment of the victim

victimSafetyEq2.label: Victim Safety Equipment 2
victimSafetyEq2.description: The safety equipment of the victim

victimEjected.label: Victim Ejected
victimEjected.description: Indicates whether the victim was ejected from the vehicle

cityAreaSqmi.label: City Area
cityAreaSqmi.description: City area (in square miles) calculated geographically

cityPopDens.label: City Population Density
cityPopDens.description: Population density in city area per square mile

cityHouDens.label: City Housing Density
cityHouDens.description: Housing density in city area per square mile

cityVehicles.label: Number of Commuting Vehicles
cityVehicles.description: Total aggregate number of city_vehicles commuting in city

cityTravelTime.label: Aggregate Travel Time to Work
cityTravelTime.description: Aggregate travel time to work in city (in  minutes)

cityMeanTravelTime.label: Mean Travel Time to work Per Vehicle
cityMeanTravelTime.description: Average travel time to work per city_vehicles (in minutes) - calculated by divinding aggregate travel time by aggregate commutting city_vehicles

roadName.label: Road Name
roadName.description: Name of the road from the road's layer

roadId.label: Road ID
roadId.description: Road ID matching from the road's layer

placeName.label: Road City
placeName.description: City of the road from the road's layer

roadCat.label: Road Category
roadCat.description: Category of the road from the road's layer

roadLength.label: Road Length (in miles)
roadLength.description: Road length from the OC Tiger/Lines layer

roadsPrimary.label: Number of Primary Road Segments
roadsPrimary.description: Number of primary road segments in the city

roadsSecondary.label: Number of Secondary Road Segments
roadsSecondary.description: Number of secondary road segments in the city

roadsLocal.label: Number of Local Road Segments
roadsLocal.description: Number of local road segments in the city

roadLengthMean.label: Mean Road Length
roadLengthMean.description: Mean road length in the city

roadLengthSum.label: Total Road Length
roadLengthSum.description: Total road length in the city

populationTotal.label: Total Population
populationTotal.description: Total population in the Census Block

housingUnitsTotal.label: Total Housing Units
housingUnitsTotal.description: Total housing units in the Census Block

householdsTotal.label: Total Households
householdsTotal.description: Total households in the Census Block

housingUnitsVacant.label: Vacant Housing Units
housingUnitsVacant.description: Vacant housing units in the Census Block

housingUnitsMortgage.label: Housing Units with Mortgage
housingUnitsMortgage.description: Owned housing units with a mortgage or a loan in the Census Block

housingUnitsOwned.label: Housing Units Owned
housingUnitsOwned.description: Owned housing units free and clear in the Census Block

housingUnitsRenterOccupied.label: Renter Occupied Housing Units
housingUnitsRenterOccupied.description: Renter occupied housing units in the Census Block

vacancyRate.label: Vacancy Rate
vacancyRate.description: Vacancy rate in the Census Block

housingUnitsOwnerOccupied.label: Owner Occupied Housing Units
housingUnitsOwnerOccupied.description: Owner occupied housing units in the Census Block

homeownershipRate.label: Homeownership Rate
homeownershipRate.description: Homeownership rate in the Census Block

populationDensity.label: Population Density
populationDensity.description: Population density in the Census Block

housingDensity.label: Housing Density
housingDensity.description: Housing density in the Census Block

latitude.label: GPS Latitude
latitude.description: Latitude of the crash location in decimal degrees. The decimal point is included. LATITUDE and LONGITUDE are from the crash report

longitude.label: GPS Longitude
longitude.description: Longitude of the crash location in decimal degrees. The decimal point is included. There is no minus sign. The longitude is understood to be West of Meridian. LATITUDE and LONGITUDE are from the crash report

pointX.label: X Coordinate Location
pointX.description: The longitude of the geocoded location, uses the World Geodetic System from 1984 (WGS84). POINT_X and POINT_Y are generated using the geociding process by UC Berkeley Safe TREC

pointY.label: Y Coordinate Location
pointY.description: The latitude of the geocoded location, uses the World Geodetic System from 1984 (WGS84). POINT_X and POINT_Y are generated using the geociding process by UC Berkeley Safe TREC

geometry.label: Geometry
geometry.varNotes: Generated by the sf R package
